languages.text: "О, снова вы! Не так много людей вообще заговаривают со мной, тем более — снова. Хотите дослушать историю?"
"Oh, it's you again! Not many people bother to talk to me in the first place, let alone twice. Do you want to hear the rest of my story?"

languages.text: “噢，您又来了！没多少人愿意来和我说话，更不用说来找我两次了。您想听我讲完剩下的故事吗？”
languages.original_text: "Oh, it's you again! Not many people bother to talk to me in the first place, let alone twice. Do you want to hear the rest of my story?"

languages.text: «Ah, ¡otra vez usted! Pocas personas se toman la molestia de hablar conmigo una vez, ¡y mucho menos dos! ¿Quiere oír cómo continúa mi historia?».
languages.original_text: "Oh, it's you again! Not many people bother to talk to me in the first place, let alone twice. Do you want to hear the rest of my story?"

languages.text: « Oh, vous revoilà ! Peu de gens se donnent la peine de venir me parler, alors deux fois, imaginez... Voulez-vous entendre la fin de mon histoire ? »

traits.locale_text: "Aa, yine siz gelmişsiniz! İnsanların çoğu değil iki kez, bir kez bile benim suratıma bakmaya tenezzül etmiyor. Acaba hikâyemin geri kalanını duymak mı istediniz?"
